responseText: NSLOCTEXT("", "55926E7747477A6BAE4FA185C574E627", "Before there were harbingers! Before there were Kings! Before there were tombstones! There was the Master Sire! It was upon this high ground that he set foot upon Verra from divine realms. Here he came to bestow his everlasting gifts upon true blooded Verrans. Here is where his celestial ashes hide among the fallen hoping to see the light of moons again.")
